					<h2><a title="Permanent Link to The Korean Peninsula in 2013 in Review" href="http://blog.keia.org/2013/12/the-korean-peninsula-in-2013-in-review/" rel="bookmark">The Korean Peninsula in 2013 in Review</a></h2>
					<p class="post_date">Posted on 31 December 2013. <span class="singletags">Tags: <a href="http://blog.keia.org/tag/china/" rel="tag">china</a>, <a href="http://blog.keia.org/tag/economics/" rel="tag">economics</a>, <a href="http://blog.keia.org/tag/fta/" rel="tag">FTA</a>, <a href="http://blog.keia.org/tag/kaesong-industrial-complex/" rel="tag">Kaesong Industrial Complex</a>, <a href="http://blog.keia.org/tag/kim-jong-un/" rel="tag">Kim Jong-un</a>, <a href="http://blog.keia.org/tag/nuclear-weapons/" rel="tag">nuclear weapons</a>, <a href="http://blog.keia.org/tag/park-geun-hye/" rel="tag">Park Geun-hye</a>, <a href="http://blog.keia.org/tag/trade/" rel="tag">trade</a></span></p>
		
					<div class="entry">
