					<h2><a title="Permanent Link to More Interesting Rumors: Jang Song Taek’s Money Man Defects and Relatives are Recalled" href="http://blog.keia.org/2013/12/more-interesting-rumors-jang-song-taeks-money-man-defects-and-relatives-are-recalled/" rel="bookmark">More Interesting Rumors: Jang Song Taek’s Money Man Defects and Relatives are Recalled</a></h2>
					<p class="post_date">Posted on 06 December 2013. <span class="singletags">Tags: <a href="http://blog.keia.org/tag/china/" rel="tag">china</a>, <a href="http://blog.keia.org/tag/diplomacy/" rel="tag">diplomacy</a>, <a href="http://blog.keia.org/tag/leadership-transition/" rel="tag">leadership transition</a></span></p>
		
